==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbred
<hw>Un*bred"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
begotten; unborn.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Thou age
<xex>unbred</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not taught or trained; -- with <xex>to</xex>.</def>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not well-bred; ill-bred.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbreech</ent>⟦br⟧
